Sentencas: Two ScYSZ electrolytes with different impurity levels were evaluated by electrochemical impedance spectroscopy using a nickel point electrode setup.
Titulo: Effects of trace elements at the Ni/ScYSZ interface in a model solid oxide fuel cell anode

Sentencas: The nickel electrodes showed lower electrode polarization resistances on the pure electrolyte than on the impure electrolyte.
Titulo: Effects of trace elements at the Ni/ScYSZ interface in a model solid oxide fuel cell anode

Sentencas: Time-of-flight secondary ion mass spectrometry was used to evaluate the electrode/electrolyte interfaces.
Titulo: Effects of trace elements at the Ni/ScYSZ interface in a model solid oxide fuel cell anode

Sentencas: Stronger signals from silica impurities in the electrode/electrolyte interface, relative to the electrolyte/gas interface, were found on the impure electrolyte than on the pure electrolyte.
Titulo: Effects of trace elements at the Ni/ScYSZ interface in a model solid oxide fuel cell anode
